36:32.277 --> 36:34.061
♪ I'm gonna rouge my knees

36:34.104 --> 36:35.976
♪ And roll my stockings down

36:38.587 --> 36:40.502
♪ And all that jazz

36:40.546 --> 36:42.330
♪ Start the car

36:42.374 --> 36:44.245
♪ I know a whoopee spot

36:44.289 --> 36:46.291
♪ Where the gin is cold

36:46.334 --> 36:48.162
♪ But the piano's hot

36:48.206 --> 36:50.208
♪ It's just a noisy hall

36:50.251 --> 36:52.297
Where there's a nightly brawl ♪

36:52.340 --> 36:53.646
♪ And all

36:54.734 --> 36:55.648
♪ That

36:57.258 --> 36:59.956
♪ Jazz

37:00.000 --> 37:02.220
I'm no stranger to scandal.

37:02.263 --> 37:03.786
That's what it means
to be a Lodge.

37:04.352 --> 37:05.962
I love my parents.

37:06.006 --> 37:07.225
And because I love them,

37:07.703 --> 37:09.488
I trusted them.

37:09.531 --> 37:13.100
And all those nefarious things
Rumordale.com
accused me of doing?

37:13.143 --> 37:14.014
Yes,

37:14.754 --> 37:15.711
I did them.

37:15.755 --> 37:17.191
I did them under duress.

37:17.931 --> 37:19.976
Because my father
threatened me.

37:20.020 --> 37:22.327
And like the good,
dutiful daughter,

37:22.370 --> 37:24.154
I did what I was told

37:24.198 --> 37:25.591
by Hiram Lodge.

37:25.634 --> 37:28.420
♪ Find a flask We're playing fast and loose ♪

37:30.552 --> 37:32.424
♪ And all that jazz

37:32.467 --> 37:35.427
♪ Right up here
Is where I store the juice ♪

37:37.472 --> 37:39.387
♪ And all that jazz

37:39.431 --> 37:40.562
♪ Come on, babe

37:40.606 --> 37:42.347
♪ We're gonna brush the sky

37:42.390 --> 37:45.741
♪ I bet you lucky Lindy
Never flew so high ♪

37:45.785 --> 37:49.310
♪ 'Cause in the stratosphere
How could he lend an ear ♪

37:49.354 --> 37:50.442
♪ To all

37:51.617 --> 37:52.487
♪ That

37:53.836 --> 37:56.839
♪ Jazz

37:56.883 --> 37:59.451
You want to know
who I'm standing with
in the upcoming trials?

38:01.148 --> 38:02.715
Neither of them.

38:02.758 --> 38:06.675
From this day forward,
I stand only with and for...

38:07.589 --> 38:08.503
myself.

38:09.417 --> 38:11.985
♪ No, I'm no one's wife

38:12.028 --> 38:15.293
♪ But, oh, I love my life

38:15.336 --> 38:18.861
♪ And all

38:18.905 --> 38:22.169
♪ That

38:23.997 --> 38:27.217
♪ Jazz

38:27.261 --> 38:28.436
♪ That jazz!

38:31.047 --> 38:32.484
[music playing]

38:35.487 --> 38:36.662
Is that your
Harvard application?

38:37.227 --> 38:38.794
It is.

38:38.838 --> 38:41.231
But I'm thinking
of making a change
before sending it in.

38:44.191 --> 38:45.497
The Lodge name is...

38:46.149 --> 38:47.020
tainted.

38:47.063 --> 38:49.414
Like Madoff. Or Corleone.

38:49.457 --> 38:51.590
But my mother's
maiden name, Gomez?

38:52.852 --> 38:54.462
I think I could work with that.

38:54.506 --> 38:56.682
So, I would be dating
Veronica Gomez now?

38:57.160 --> 38:58.074
Mmm-hmm.

38:58.118 --> 39:00.076
Yeah? What's she like?

39:00.120 --> 39:01.164
I don't know.

39:02.340 --> 39:03.341
We're going to find out.

39:09.172 --> 39:10.696
Why, what's the matter,
Ms. Bell?

39:11.523 --> 39:12.828
Just be careful, Cheryl.

39:13.438 --> 39:14.613
[bees buzzing]

39:16.702 --> 39:18.573
Golly, what a mess.

39:18.617 --> 39:20.053
Hope you aren't allergic,
Mr. Honey.

39:21.881 --> 39:23.012
Toodles.

39:23.056 --> 39:24.274
[buzzing continues]

39:26.233 --> 39:27.713
What's happening?
Have you heard from Mom?

39:28.061 --> 39:28.888
No.

39:29.454 --> 39:30.629
Maybe I was wrong,

39:30.672 --> 39:31.717
maybe we should
roll the dice with Kevin.

39:34.197 --> 39:35.068
Um...

39:35.111 --> 39:38.506
I already have.

39:38.550 --> 39:40.595
I gave him the name
of our fake witness,

39:40.639 --> 39:41.727
Penelope Blossom.

39:43.468 --> 39:45.252
Betty...

39:45.295 --> 39:48.037
You didn't say anything
about Alice, did you?

39:52.085 --> 39:53.652
You revealed the name

39:53.695 --> 39:58.352
of an active
undercover FBI agent
to a screwed-up kid? Why?

39:58.396 --> 40:00.049
Because I trust Kevin. Okay?

40:00.093 --> 40:01.442
I wanted to be honest with him.

40:01.486 --> 40:04.227
-He will find out where Edgar--
-Betty, it worked.

40:05.664 --> 40:06.665
Kev, you're back.

40:06.708 --> 40:07.709
-Hey.
-[Kevin] Yeah.

40:07.753 --> 40:09.276
I, uh...
I connected with Fangs,

40:10.103 --> 40:11.409
told him about
Penelope Blossom,

40:11.452 --> 40:12.888
and he led me to where
the Farm is staying.

40:12.932 --> 40:16.588
It's an abandoned motel
beyond the maple barrens.

40:16.631 --> 40:18.503
Okay. Did you see my mom?
Is she okay?

40:18.546 --> 40:20.243
Uh, I didn't. I'm sorry.

40:20.287 --> 40:21.636
But I did see Edgar,

40:21.680 --> 40:23.203
and, Betty, he's armed.

40:23.246 --> 40:27.686
There were guns, and
he's building something, and...

40:27.729 --> 40:28.730
Edgar's digging in.

40:29.731 --> 40:31.037
He's getting ready for war.

40:31.080 --> 40:32.125
Well, we have to go.

40:33.343 --> 40:34.954
We have to get in there
and save our mom.

40:41.047 --> 40:42.091
[TV playing]

40:42.135 --> 40:43.266
[FP] Well, well, well.

40:44.137 --> 40:45.399
[sighs]

40:46.487 --> 40:47.488
Do I look like a jerk?

40:47.532 --> 40:48.924
No, you look like a gentleman.

40:52.537 --> 40:54.669
Stonewall's not too far,
and I'll be back every weekend.

40:55.540 --> 40:57.019
[FP] Hey...

40:57.063 --> 40:59.282
I'm glad you accepted
Chipping's offer.

40:59.326 --> 41:01.546
You're a sort of
a legacy there, you know?

41:01.589 --> 41:02.764
What do you mean?

41:02.808 --> 41:04.853
Well, your grandpa,
Forsythe the First,

41:04.897 --> 41:07.377
actually went to Stonewall Prep
for a couple of months
until he dropped out.

41:07.813 --> 41:08.857
What happened?

41:08.901 --> 41:10.337
Why didn't you
tell me this sooner?

41:10.380 --> 41:11.512
[FP] It's ancient history.

41:11.556 --> 41:13.645
But he quit at everything,
including me.

41:13.688 --> 41:15.821
He went out
for a pack of smokes,
and he never came back.

41:16.299 --> 41:17.518
Anyway...

41:17.562 --> 41:19.520
I didn't mention it because

41:19.564 --> 41:21.130
I wanted this to be
your decision,

41:21.174 --> 41:23.872
without my old man's shadow
hanging over you.

41:23.916 --> 41:25.700
It's a chance for you
to do something good,

41:25.744 --> 41:27.310
for yourself,
and I'm proud of you, son.

41:29.095 --> 41:30.009
It's going to be a good year.

41:30.705 --> 41:31.837
Really good year.

41:35.580 --> 41:36.842
-[all shouting] Jughead!
-[dogs barking]

41:37.190 --> 41:38.931
Jughead!

41:38.974 --> 41:39.975
Jug!

41:40.019 --> 41:41.150
Jug!

41:41.194 --> 41:42.587
[all] Jughead!

41:45.459 --> 41:46.721
[all continue shouting]

41:48.201 --> 41:49.289
Jughead!
